Package: ROpenWeather
Type: Package
Title: Package for downloading weather information from
    OpenWeatherMap.org
Version: 1.0
Date: 2013-06-29
Author: Adam Edgley
Maintainer: Adam Edgley<adam.edgley@gmail.com>
Description: Queries the OpenWeatherMap.org API for current and historical
    weather information. This package uses S4 classes, and provides plotting
    objects with ggplot
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    RJSONIO,
    ggplot2,
    methods
Imports:
    stats,
    utils,
    graphics
Packaged: 2013-07-11 12:21:09 UTC; adam
